    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Peel and cut your <strong>red onion[s] </strong>into wedges</p>",
