      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with the <strong>tomato wedges</strong>,<strong> onion wedges </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Add your<strong> ras el hanout</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric </strong>(save the rest for later!), 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 3,
