    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 22-25 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the veg is tender – this is your <strong>oven-baked Moroccan-style chicken </strong>and<strong> roasted veg</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
