    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip your <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems, discard the stems</p><p>Once the couscous is tender, stir through the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and tear over the <strong>mint leaves</strong></p><p>Crumble over <strong>half</strong> your <strong>feta </strong>(save the rest for garnish!), season with a very generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy giant couscous</strong></p>",
