      "instruction": "<p>To serve, top the <strong>creamy giant couscous </strong>with the<strong> oven-baked</strong> <strong>Moroccan-Style chicken </strong>and<strong> roasted veg</strong></p><p>Drizzle over any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>roasting juices </strong>from the tray[s] and crumble over the <strong>remaining feta</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
